"Home," Vulois said in a sullen voice, "It leads back to Cybertron! 
CYBERTRON!" Vulois hugged the strange bot, and than turned to 
Windrazor and Child.

"Do you know what this means? Once are mission is complete, we don't 
have to travel in a ship for years and years! We can just go here! We 
can do this!!!!"

Vulois went to Beast Mode and flew around in circles for a bit. he 
than landed, exhausted.

"Wheew! Sorry there, it's just this has made my mission alot easier. 
COme on, let's get back to the embassy."

Vulois took off.
